Radio class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "GroupClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Radio class is used to create radio gadgets.

  You must pass in Entries a string made of the entries of the
  radio gadget separated by | .

  See @{"MakeObj()" LINK "Functions.guide/MakeObj"}.

